<paragraph id="8BA936F9FFC0FFD5FF07FDD1FCA1FD57" blockId="2.[166,874,623,645]" box="[166,874,623,645]" pageId="2" pageNumber="375">Fig. 5. Head and prothorax lateral aspect, prosternum indicated by arrow.</paragraph>
